[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[1m\u001b[36mTrey Roberts\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m•\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m2026-03-04\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m9d ago\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n      Meeting tmw with Ben Chayer (VP, Product) - the business DMer and the boss of our champion, James Campeau (Sr. Dir., Product)\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "      Meeting Objective: Solidify Agents as an immediate starting place for Master Group\r\n      - Position Agents as initial solution to prove out Pricefx Value over next ~5months\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "      -\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "      - Create runway for expansion in Q4 (and expected budget for POM in '27)\r\n      -\r\n      AGENDA - Tailored for Exec audience\r\n      - Platform Overview + Why Agents First\r\n      -\r\n      - Agents Demo\r\n      -\r\n      - Master Roadmap - what do the next 6months entail\r\n      -\r\n      - Agents Commercials & Next Steps\r\n      -\r\n      INTENDED OUTCOME: Approval to present Agents value case to CIO for signoff\r\n\r\n  \u001b[2m━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[1m\u001b[36mSuzi Rodriguez\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m•\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m2026-02-27\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m14d ago\u001b[0m  \u001b[1m\u001b[33m NINJA UPDATE \u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "      2/27 - \u001b[1m\u001b[32m@Trey Roberts\u001b[0m , \u001b[1m\u001b[32m@Christopher Kleemann\u001b[0m , and I attended a call with James today. He let us know that their budget had been slashed, but\r\n      we were able to turn the conversation around into Agents only first and we discussed easy options with low integration efforts to get them\r\n      using the platform right away, get into Platform Manager second to start the data flow between Infor and Pfx, which sets them up for success\r\n      for future expansion. James liked the idea of being able to provide value to his internal teams through Agents so he can then prove how much\r\n      more value the full solution can bring their org.\r\n      Follow up demo scheduled for 3/3 for James and additional leaders to see a generic agents demo.\r\n      (NINJA UPDATE)\r\n\r\n"]
