[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[2m          Next Step\u001b[0m  \u001b[1m\u001b[33m05 Feb- Agents second readout with impact analysis being planned for week 3 of Feb.   29.01 - Delay in decision cycle due to data\u001b[0m\r\n                       \u001b[1m\u001b[33mdeletion issue. 19 Jan - Agents discussion still going strong while focus remains on restoration of data.\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m            Opp Age\u001b[0m  \u001b[36m8mo 5d\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2m     Stage Duration\u001b[0m  \u001b[36m5mo 15d\u001b[0m\r\n"]
